object.customQuery:
select 
		b.systemid,
		b.cmmcontainer,
		b.parentid,
	case
		when b.distancetoshore like 'More Than 10 Miles%' then '10'
		when b.distancetoshore like '%Mile%' then
			 ltrim(rtrim(substring(b.distancetoshore, instr(b.distancetoshore, '-')+ 2, instr(b.distancetoshore, 'M')- instr(b.distancetoshore, '-')-3)))
		when distancetoshore like '%Mi' then
			 ltrim(rtrim(substring(b.distancetoshore, instr(b.distancetoshore, '-')+ 2, instr(b.distancetoshore, 'M')- instr(b.distancetoshore, '-')-3)))
		when distancetoshore like '%mi' then
			 ltrim(rtrim(substring(b.distancetoshore, instr(b.distancetoshore, '-')+ 2, instr(b.distancetoshore, 'm')- instr(b.distancetoshore, '-')-3)))
		else null
	end as distancetoshoreMile,
	case
		when b.distancetoshore like '%Feet%' then
  			ltrim(rtrim(substring(b.distancetoshore, instr(b.distancetoshore, '-')+ 2, instr(b.distancetoshore, 'F')- instr(b.distancetoshore, '-')-3)))
		else null
	end as distancetoshoreFeet,
		b.PurchasedLast12Months,
		b.wiringcd,
		b.plumbingcd,
		b.heatingcd,
		b.roofingcd,
		b.roofingyear,
		b.sqft,
		b.msbrctreconstructioncost,
		b.accountcreditind,
		b.jewelrylimit,
		b.id,
		b.homeautocreditdescription,
		b.BldgNumber,
		b.H107Ind as building_application_h107_indicator,
		b.Tier as building_application_tier,
	    b.NumOfFamilies,
		b.ProtectionClass,
		b.YearBuilt,
		b.WiringYear,
		b.HeatingYear,
		b.PlumbingYear,
		b.TypeOfBusinessOne,
		b.MotorizedLandConveyanceDesp
   from building b
   join advrxxchangedbeans
     on b.CMMContainer = advrxxchangedbeans.CMMContainer
    and b.SystemId = advrxxchangedbeans.SystemId
  where b.cmmcontainer = 'Application'
    and concat(advrxxchangedbeans.adddt,advrxxchangedbeans.addtm)>='$$m_strdt' 
    and concat(advrxxchangedbeans.adddt,advrxxchangedbeans.addtm) <='$$m_enddt'
